Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.12,0:00:18.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 来的真早啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.74,0:00:21.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这店还是这么的不景气啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.30,0:00:22.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,废话真多
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.81,0:00:24.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚上可是很热闹的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.02,0:00:31.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,于是 那个照片 是怎么一回事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.48,0:00:36.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说来话长了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.09,0:00:39.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个 你知道么
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.33,0:00:43.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,游戏？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.46,0:00:44.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「AmuSphere」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.16,0:00:47.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「NERvGear」后继机型对应的MMO
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.98,0:00:52.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 它和SAO一样是VRMMO么
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.98,0:00:52.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs28}VRMMO：大型虚拟网络游戏
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.89,0:00:56.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ALfheim Online
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.02,0:00:59.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎发音为ALfheim
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.04,0:01:02.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,意思是妖精的国家
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.46,0:01:04.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妖精…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.63,0:01:14.79,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隠してた感情が　悲鳴を上げている
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.63,0:01:14.79,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隐藏起来的感情在呐喊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.81,0:01:20.40,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確かな誓いを手に
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.81,0:01:20.40,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手中紧握坚定的誓言
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.80,0:01:35.87,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇跡だけを求め
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.80,0:01:35.87,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只想乞求一个奇迹
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.89,0:01:41.15,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消えない闇を彷徨う
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.89,0:01:41.15,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彷徨在消失不尽的黑暗中
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.17,0:01:46.35,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ここに入れば　二度と
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.17,0:01:46.35,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进入这里的话
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.37,0:01:51.73,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,未来見ることできない
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.37,0:01:51.73,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眼前又将失去未来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.80,0:01:54.38,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今宵も月が誘うって
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.80,0:01:54.38,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今宵也有月来相邀
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.40,0:01:56.97,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,まだ言葉出さないけど
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.40,0:01:56.97,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想说的话仍未传达
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.99,0:02:01.12,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心の中叫び続けた
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.99,0:02:01.12,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但却在心中不停的回荡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.05,0:02:07.19,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隠してた感情が　悲鳴を上げている
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.05,0:02:07.19,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隐藏起来的感情在呐喊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.21,0:02:12.40,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確かな誓いを手に
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.21,0:02:12.40,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手中紧握坚定的誓言
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.42,0:02:17.95,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,後ほんの少しだけ強くなれてなら
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.42,0:02:17.95,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要再稍微坚强一点
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.97,0:02:21.67,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,何の前にある この空
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.97,0:02:21.67,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不论前方将要面对什么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.69,0:02:24.56,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超えて行くから
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.69,0:02:24.56,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先从超越这片天空开始
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.01,0:02:29.58,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,この先にある未来に
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.01,0:02:29.58,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向着前方的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.60,0:02:32.77,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手を伸ばすから
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.60,0:02:32.77,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伸出双手
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.99,0:02:41.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs60\c&HE1BE56&\3c&H080808&\bord1\pos(517,458)\be2}妖精们的国家
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.51,0:02:44.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妖精的国家吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.22,0:02:46.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是休闲类的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.73,0:02:49.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 好像不是哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.98,0:02:52.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全技巧制
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.42,0:02:53.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重视玩家技巧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.80,0:02:55.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,推荐PK
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.69,0:02:56.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全技巧制？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.27,0:02:59.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说没有等级存在
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.10,0:03:03.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各种技巧通过反复使用就能增强
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.47,0:03:06.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战斗也依存于玩家的运动能力
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.77,0:03:08.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可真难啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.60,0:03:12.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是没有剑技 而是使用魔法的SAO
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.74,0:03:15.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个现在可是很有人气的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.69,0:03:18.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,理由就是 可以飞
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.34,0:03:19.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以飞？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.61,0:03:21.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为是妖精 所以是有翅膀的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.90,0:03:23.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它上面搭载了飞行引擎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.10,0:03:26.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,熟练掌握后就可以自由的飞行了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.74,0:03:29.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个要怎么控制呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.44,0:03:30.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.79,0:03:32.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过貌似很困难呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.43,0:03:34.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是当然啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.05,0:03:37.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毕竟是要操纵人类并不存在的翅膀嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.30,0:03:40.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能是用背后的肌肉来操作吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.38,0:03:45.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,于是 这个大人气的游戏
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.43,0:03:47.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟亚丝娜有什么关系呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.23,0:03:51.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么看
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.82,0:03:55.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很像… 亚丝娜
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.70,0:03:57.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你果然也这么认为吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.51,0:03:58.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赶快告诉我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.89,0:04:00.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个是在哪拍的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.51,0:04:02.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,游戏里面哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.43,0:04:04.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「ALfheim Online」里面
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.87,0:04:08.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个似乎叫做 世界树
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.17,0:04:11.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这棵树的上面有一个传说中的城堡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.82,0:04:15.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玩家被分成9个不同的种族
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.75,0:04:19.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,互相比拼着 看哪个种族能第一个到达城堡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.43,0:04:22.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飞上去不就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.47,0:04:24.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像因为有什么滞空时间
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.91,0:04:26.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以不能一直飞在空中
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.19,0:04:30.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,于是这时 出现了5个玩家按体型顺序叠罗汉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.27,0:04:33.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用多段火箭式方法飞了一次
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.52,0:04:35.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.01,0:04:37.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然样子很蠢 但想法还不错啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.44,0:04:41.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使这样 他们也只到达了世界树最下端的树枝
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.34,0:04:44.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们拍了几张照片
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.63,0:04:47.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其中一张 出现了个稀奇的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.99,0:04:50.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸟笼？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.89,0:04:53.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(450,450)\be3\blur3\an8\fs26}本片字幕由异域字幕组(www.yydm.com)制作,仅供试看之用,如果喜欢本作品,请购买并支持正版!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.56,0:04:53.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把这个鸟笼的解像度放大到极限后
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.06,0:04:59.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(450,450)\be3\blur3\an8\fs26}翻译 永 天井 步 明撒 童话 时间 鹿 压制 A4
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.25,0:04:56.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这个了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.25,0:05:00.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 为什么亚丝娜会在这个游戏里
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.22,0:05:04.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「RCT」出品
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.77,0:05:10.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说 明日奈生命是由我在维持着
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.79,0:05:16.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾基尔 这个游戏能给我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.93,0:05:19.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是可以 你要去么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.83,0:05:21.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要亲眼去看看
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.67,0:05:25.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死了可以复活的游戏 简直是小菜一碟
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.76,0:05:32.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得去买硬件呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.15,0:05:34.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「NERvGear」就可以运行哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.18,0:05:39.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「AmuSphere」只是「NERvGear」的安全强化版而已
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.67,0:05:40.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这倒是方便了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.50,0:05:43.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要把亚丝娜救出来哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.03,0:05:47.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不这样的话 我们的战斗是不会结束的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.72,0:05:50.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 总有一天要在这里开线下通关庆功会
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.24,0:06:08.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我这个笨蛋笨蛋笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.75,0:06:09.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.47,0:06:12.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.34,0:06:26.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.00,0:06:33.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我… 我还以为会死呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.10,0:06:35.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是个慌里慌张的家伙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.32,0:06:36.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢点吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.65,0:06:41.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小直 关于昨晚的事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.83,0:06:43.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.14,0:06:46.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个… 怎么说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.16,0:06:48.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.69,0:06:52.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多亏了小直 我又重新打起精神了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.73,0:06:54.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会放弃的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.16,0:06:57.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对会把明日奈夺回来的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.31,0:07:02.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯… 加油啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.30,0:07:04.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也想见见明日奈姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.00,0:07:07.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们一定会相处得很好的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.22,0:07:10.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 等会见
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.63,0:07:28.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结婚仪式在一周后的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.35,0:07:31.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1月26日于这个病房举行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.93,0:07:33.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也会请你的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.39,0:07:37.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再一次 借给我力量吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.49,0:07:50.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Link Start
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.10,0:08:05.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎来到AlFheim Online
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.34,0:08:11.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先 请输入人物的性别及姓名
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.08,0:08:18.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此 你就是那位英雄桐人君吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.60,0:08:26.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(桐人 男)
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.31,0:08:31.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来 请选择您的种族
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.00,0:08:34.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请从九个种族中选择一个
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.82,0:08:40.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这个吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.24,0:08:43.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您选择了守卫精灵「spriggan」
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.46,0:08:47.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,角色外貌将随机生成 可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.62,0:08:53.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么现在 您将被传送到守卫精灵的主城镇
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.73,0:08:56.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祝您好运
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.92,0:09:23.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.92,0:09:31.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又发生什么事啦？！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.36,0:09:46.78,biaoshi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\be2\blur3\pos(510,461)}ALFheim·中立区域·古森
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.46,0:10:03.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又来到这里了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.09,0:10:07.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明碰上过那种事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.01,0:10:11.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来 这里是哪里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.43,0:10:24.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.39,0:10:25.63,biaoshi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(373,282)\frz6.953\3c&HF5EBDA&\c&HA29084&\shad0\fad(300,0)}在野外无法立刻下线 确认选择吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.38,0:10:32.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 看看人物状态
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.04,0:10:34.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs28}种族 守卫精灵 生命力 400 魔力   800 技能 单手剑 1000
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.02,0:10:38.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是怎么回事 出BUG了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.65,0:10:45.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶 这和SAO时的参数相同
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.25,0:10:48.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.31,0:10:51.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是在SAO里面吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.18,0:10:57.69,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(280,323)\c&HFDFEFF&\3c&H14AEF5&\shad0}道具
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.32,0:11:01.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.58,0:11:05.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了… 一定要有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.54,0:11:50.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我啊 结衣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.92,0:11:51.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还记得我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.38,0:11:58.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸 又见面了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.57,0:11:59.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.40,0:12:02.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结衣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.86,0:12:05.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.12,0:12:08.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肚子饿了吧 我们吃饭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.70,0:12:09.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.29,0:12:18.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.10,0:12:21.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈 爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.98,0:12:26.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸 爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.17,0:12:29.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.65,0:12:33.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇迹发生了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.04,0:12:49.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说 这究竟是怎么回事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.70,0:12:53.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的意思是 这里并不是SAO的世界呀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.32,0:12:56.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是个叫做「ALfheim Online」的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.24,0:12:57.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别的游戏世界里
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.31,0:13:01.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微等一下哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.40,0:13:08.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个世界 是SAO服务器的拷贝
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.69,0:13:09.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拷贝？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.92,0:13:10.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.10,0:13:15.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基本程序和图像形式是和SAO完全相同的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.72,0:13:19.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是 主系统的版本稍微旧了点
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.14,0:13:27.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,运营SAO的ARGUS的事后处理 都被委托给了RCT
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.54,0:13:28.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.49,0:13:33.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,RCT吸收了ARGUS的技术资产 并将它挪用了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.61,0:13:36.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 为什么我的个人数据还被保留着呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.31,0:13:40.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下 让我看一下爸爸的数据
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.13,0:13:49.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有错呢 这就是爸爸在SAO里使用过的角色数据
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.97,0:13:52.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为这两个世界里的存档资料格式基本相同
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.32,0:13:57.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以两个世界共通的技能熟练度才会被继承吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.38,0:14:01.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来 二刀流技能不见了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.89,0:14:05.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,道具也… 好像都损坏了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.86,0:14:08.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在被勘误程序检测出来之前
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.28,0:14:09.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是赶紧扔掉比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.40,0:14:11.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.96,0:14:17.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\3c&HF5EBDA&\c&HA29084&\shad0\fad(0,0)\pos(603,86)\frz2.758}提示
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.03,0:14:17.46,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA29084&\shad0\fad(300,0)\frz2.564\pos(531,296)\3c&HEFE3DA&}要删除全部道具吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.91,0:14:31.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 技能熟练度怎么办呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.85,0:14:36.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关于技能 只要不是人工GM亲自确认
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.65,0:14:37.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就应该没有问题
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.10,0:14:39.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这… 这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.98,0:14:42.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这下子已经不是封闭者
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.18,0:14:44.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是纯粹的作弊者了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.66,0:14:47.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结衣 在这个世界里是什么身份呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.93,0:14:53.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个… 辅助玩家的模拟人格程序
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.02,0:14:56.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被划分到「导航精灵」这类里了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.22,0:15:10.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个是我作为「导航精灵」的姿态
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.37,0:15:14.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很痒的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.30,0:15:18.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 你还和以前一样有管理员权限吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.66,0:15:21.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有 现在能做到的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.44,0:15:25.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有查询和连接广域地图数据而已
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.49,0:15:26.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.59,0:15:28.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事实上
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.20,0:15:30.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里… 亚丝娜
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.38,0:15:32.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的妈妈好像在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.17,0:15:34.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？ 妈妈在？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.98,0:15:36.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是怎么一回事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.14,0:15:39.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚丝娜在SAO通关之后
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.81,0:15:41.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并没有回到现实世界
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.62,0:15:44.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我得到的情报
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.57,0:15:47.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说在ALfheim里有人看到过和亚丝娜很像的人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.96,0:15:49.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.15,0:15:52.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经知道她大概在哪里了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.12,0:15:55.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是一个叫做「世界树」的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.91,0:15:57.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该就是那个吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.94,0:16:00.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈 在那里吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.17,0:16:06.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.55,0:16:09.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我为什么会在这种毫无人烟的森林里登录啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.49,0:16:13.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该是被传送到主城镇才对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.14,0:16:17.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不清楚…可能是因为位置情报损坏了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.79,0:16:19.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或者是因为混线了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.19,0:16:20.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与其掉在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.07,0:16:24.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还不如让我掉在世界树附近的好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.46,0:16:30.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是翅膀啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.39,0:16:32.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要怎样才能飞起来呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.98,0:16:35.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像有辅助控制杆
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.43,0:16:37.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伸出左手
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.86,0:16:40.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做出握住东西的姿势试试看
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.49,0:16:48.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 向里拉是上升
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.29,0:16:49.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向下压是下降
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.86,0:16:51.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,左右是旋转
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.99,0:17:01.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,按下按钮是加速 松开则是减速
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.88,0:17:07.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翅膀发光的这段时间是可以飞行的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.08,0:17:10.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,经过一段时间之后
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.19,0:17:13.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必须让翅膀休息才行
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.81,0:17:23.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此 我大致明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.42,0:17:26.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之 距离这里最近的城镇在哪里呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.11,0:17:28.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西边有一个属于风精灵「sylphid」的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.96,0:17:31.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫做司伊鲁班的城镇
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.49,0:17:32.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那里是离这最近的…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.70,0:17:35.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.80,0:17:37.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有玩家就在附近
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.50,0:17:57.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉… 莉法
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.77,0:17:58.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.19,0:18:00.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油啊雷根
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.11,0:18:02.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这样一路逃到风精灵的领地的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.32,0:18:05.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷根 快避开
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.33,0:18:11.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 真够烦人的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.57,0:18:13.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没办法了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.78,0:18:16.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,准备战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.15,0:18:18.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶 打不赢的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.49,0:18:20.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是西格鲁特他们 肯定也…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.32,0:18:23.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会尽量多拖住几个人的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.41,0:18:25.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你至少得想办法打落一个
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.60,0:18:26.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会挂彩的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.73,0:18:29.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偶尔也要让我看到你帅气的一面吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.11,0:18:52.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.36,0:19:03.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样下去能赢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.16,0:19:08.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋 别停下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.66,0:19:12.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.17,0:19:15.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷根
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.18,0:19:46.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不住了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.50,0:19:48.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过这是我们的任务
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.83,0:19:51.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把钱和道具留下的话 就放你一马
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.55,0:19:53.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,装哪门子的绅士啊 影宗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.05,0:19:56.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久没有女人当对手了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.63,0:19:58.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干脆杀了她吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.54,0:20:03.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算死我也绝对要再拉一个人陪葬
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.72,0:20:06.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不怕死亡惩罚的人就放马过来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.32,0:20:08.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是个倔强的女孩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.53,0:20:10.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就没办法了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.93,0:20:36.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,疼疼疼…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.60,0:20:41.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这算是着陆失误了吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.23,0:20:49.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还愣着做什么 快点逃走啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.10,0:20:53.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三个重战士袭击一个女孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.01,0:20:55.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有点不太光彩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.18,0:20:57.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你算哪根葱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.80,0:21:00.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新手也敢大摇大摆的出来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.70,0:21:07.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就如你所愿 送你归西
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.27,0:21:18.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什……！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.77,0:21:20.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我扔
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.84,0:21:29.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说 这些人可以砍吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.08,0:21:32.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应… 应该是没问题的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.56,0:21:36.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少对方是这么打算的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.96,0:21:38.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我就失礼啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.79,0:21:48.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.69,0:22:04.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来该轮到谁呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.72,0:22:09.39,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高く　高く
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.72,0:22:09.39,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高一点 再高一点
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.42,0:22:12.72,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,この手を伸ばして
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.42,0:22:12.72,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将这双手伸向那里
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.74,0:22:16.55,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,きっと　きっとで
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.74,0:22:16.55,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定 一定会
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.57,0:22:22.67,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,もう一度願うから
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.57,0:22:22.67,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再一次许下愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.69,0:22:37.27,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,止め処ない思いは
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.69,0:22:37.27,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无止境的思念
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.29,0:22:40.78,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日常に呑まれて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.29,0:22:40.78,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被日常的生活吞没
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.90,0:22:47.99,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,揺らめきながら　未だ形も変えていた
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.90,0:22:47.99,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在不断的摇曳中 形状也在改变着
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.01,0:22:51.51,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今更もう遅いかな
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.01,0:22:51.51,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在是不是已经太晚了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.53,0:22:55.04,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,返事はない自問自答
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.53,0:22:55.04,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自知不会得到回复的自问自答
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.17,0:22:58.31,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,すべてそう自分次第
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.17,0:22:58.31,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到头来做决定的还是自己
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.33,0:23:02.93,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終わりも　始まりも
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.33,0:23:02.93,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不论开始 还是结束
